             was indicted for <rs id="t18070408-51-off300" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070408-51-off300" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070408-51-off300" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18070408-51-cd301" type="crimeDate">21st of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070408-51-off300 t18070408-51-cd301"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070408-51-off302 t18070408-51-cd301"></join>, eighteen shovels, value 1 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18070408-51-victim468" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Haskins
