                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070408-51-defend466 t18070408-51-punish307"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>BRITTAIN, <rs id="t18070408-51-verdict308" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070408-51-verdict308" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
